The version should also be checked and if the version has changed, the migration should be re-executed.
# Ultra-Simple Migration Framework with Version-Based Re-Execution

Let's refine our migration framework to re-execute migrations when their version changes. This is a common pattern to handle updates to existing migrations.

## 1. Enhanced Single YAML Configuration

The YAML file remains the same, with version information being used for re-execution decisions:

```yaml
